# Project Title
- JWT Json Web Token and verify Roles with node js
## Introduction
- basic authentication hash password when create user and write file to create users Database 
- technology used: express-> create server, cookieParser to use cookie middleware, 
## Installation
- cd node_jwt_verifyRoles
- npm install
- npm run dev
## Usage
- step 1 create user
- step 2 login with basic authentication 
- step 3 get resources user by get accessToken when we login and send it to verify jwt 
- step 4 logout to remove accessToken and cookie
